comment: This is a very cute top, it has nice material, it is soft and very comfy. I love the vneck and I agree with another person's review the collar makes it look a bit Matronly. It is a medium weight and a good amount of stretch. I ordered the size XXL (I'm a 37 in bust) and right now, that is my normal size, sometimes I can fit in a 1x. It is very accurate with the chest measurements with a tad extra material around the armpit/chest area. Not too much but I may be able to go one size smaller as I do not have a broad shoulders, I do have larger upper arms and it fits very comfortable in that area. Because of the stretch it does fit a bit roomy but it falls nicely so you don't notice it too much. I find I have to pull it down on and off as it rides up a tad in the back, but since I have a generous booty that may be the reason why. Either way I'm still very comfortable in it.
